        <item>
            <title>中国网上现大量「假」盗版《黑神话：悟空》    下载后竟是《西游记》电视剧和正版购买连结</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/china-piracy-blackmythwukong/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=china-piracy-blackmythwukong</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/china-piracy-blackmythwukong/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 11:44:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[盗版游戏]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[西游记]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[黑神话：悟空]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1257913</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">《黑神话：悟空》推出后登上了 Steam 平台上畅销游戏和最多人游玩的榜首，在游戏热卖的同时有人发现有利可图，在网上交易平台出售盗版的《黑神话：悟空》。盗版游戏通常都比官方定价稍低，但有中国网民则发现有不少是远低于官方定价，标榜「1 元畅玩黑悟空」。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1257920 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/351-scaled-e1724324927672-284x580.jpg" alt="" width="284" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/351-scaled-e1724324927672-284x580.jpg 284w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/351-scaled-e1724324927672-441x900.jpg 441w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/351-scaled-e1724324927672.jpg 1232w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 284px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_28484764">澎湃</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">目前在 Steam 平台上《黑神话：悟空》的定价为 298 港币（中国为 268 人民币）。网上出售盗版游戏的方式大致分成两种，一种是利用 Steam 的离线登录或亲友收藏库同享游戏的功能，严格上属于钻漏洞而非盗版。另一种则是从商家提供的连结下载盗版游戏，解压缩后便可直接游玩。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1257923 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/353-e1724324743950-350x580.jpg" alt="" width="350" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/353-e1724324743950-350x580.jpg 350w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/353-e1724324743950-543x900.jpg 543w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/353-e1724324743950.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 350px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_28484764">澎湃</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">这名内地网民就挑选了其中最便宜的来购买，只需花费 1 毫子人民币。根据商家所提供的连结，档案的大小为 120 GB 比官方的 118 GB 还要大，用 3 小时才将其下载完成。打开游戏后竟跳过了正版会出现的正版游戏阅读协议和调整亮度的步骤，直接出现了游戏科学 Gamescience 的标志，但总算成功进入游戏主画面。点击「设置」后竟弹出「更新显卡驱动」的提示，直接开始游戏又会出现各种故障，更会出现「蓝画面」。但原来只是一张「蓝画面」的图片，后来就会弹出各大平台购买正版《黑神话：悟空》的连结。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1257944 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123-15-428x580.jpg" alt="" width="428" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123-15-428x580.jpg 428w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/123-15.jpg 664w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 428px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1257927 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/359-e1724324821446-694x369.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/359-e1724324821446-694x369.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/359-e1724324821446-1280x680.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/359-e1724324821446.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1257929 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/360-e1724324841263-694x362.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/360-e1724324841263-694x362.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/360-e1724324841263-1280x667.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/360-e1724324841263.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_28484764">澎湃</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">原本这一切都是热心网民为了打击盗版游戏猖獗的奇招，原来一直的游戏画面都只是影片，甚至有些商家出售的《黑神话：悟空》实际为 1986 年的 4K 《西游记》电视剧全集。购买盗版游戏的玩家花费了 1 毫子和几个小时下载游戏，换来了要购买正版游戏的教训，这位商家甚至会将 1 毫子退款给买家支持他购买正版的《黑神话：悟空》。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1257935 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dbb357fa8f86c12f0f3a-694x339.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dbb357fa8f86c12f0f3a-694x339.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dbb357fa8f86c12f0f3a.jpg 728w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/66757/chinese-pirated-black-myth-wukong-lure-illegal-players?fbclid=IwY2xjawEz7vRleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHb0r9Oh2SCGB4TM-PGTG5x0f1drrMEkhLKE4pgf1fV2-oMGdAQ5lv-CXsA_aem_uYD32f0sdGxPKkgXBY-gkQ">4Gamers</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_28484764">澎湃</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/flydigi-apex-4-black-myth-wukong-gaming-controller/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《黑神话：悟空》热潮停不了   Flydigi Apex 4 特别版游戏手掣发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/wukung-china-govt/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">外交部回应《黑神话：悟空》大卖　发言人：从名字来看反映中国文化吸引力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/blackmythwukong-steam-most-played-game/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国公司批员工放假玩《黑神话：悟空》 买 Game 钱更可报销</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/china-piracy-blackmythwukong/game-channel/">中国网上现大量「假」盗版《黑神话：悟空》    下载后竟是《西游记》电视剧和正版购买连结</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
