        <item>
            <title>【评测】模寿 x BLITZWAY 真三一万能侠　LED 灯效惊艳 + 跳齿式关节</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/moshowtoysblitzwaygetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=moshowtoysblitzwaygetter</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/moshowtoysblitzwaygetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:30:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256633</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年来，真三一万能侠合金 Figure 大家都见得多了，多厂也相继有推出各自有独特风格的版本，而今次最新推出的是由模寿与 BLITZWAY 合作，真三一万能侠合金 Figure，售价为人民币$980，折合约港币$1,100 左右，确实引起了不少关注，而这个版本又有什么特点呢？小编已收到送测版本，立即为大家开箱。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0644-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">当然又是大大盒的了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_0643-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">极具份量，整箱重 5.2KG。</p><p>外观设计方面，这款真三一万能侠相当忠于原作。最为人瞩目的是其标志性的「水桶腰」造型，线条简洁有力。表面采用高光泽度处理，尤其是红色部分，呈现出类似跑车烤漆的质感，视觉效果十分抢眼。然而，这种处理也带来了一些小问题，如容易留下指纹，需要经常擦拭保养。头部设计亦相当出色，不仅还原了真三一万能侠锐利的眼神，还提供了多种可替换的表情部件，虽然效果不是特别明显，但也体现了制作团队的用心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-694x510.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="510" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-694x510.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0303-scaled.jpg 1226w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-694x407.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="407" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-694x407.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0356-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0318" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938406694/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938406694_2d58069163_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0318" width="1024" height="688" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0327" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323858/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323858_304de9c8e8_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0327" width="1024" height="601" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0319" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938073516/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938073516_04cfd7b039_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0319" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0322-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0323-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0325-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0313-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0314-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>灯光效果是这部真三一万能侠的一大特色。头部、胸口、腰部和手臂等多个部位都配备了 LED 灯组，可说是全身都可亮齐灯光效果，电池方面就要用到 AG1 及 AG13 电池，每种需要 8 粒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-694x455.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-694x455.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0307-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0310-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0311-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>由于今次是测试版，尚有地方会再作改良，例如手腕装 LED 位置的扣位，会有扣不稳的情况掉下，厂方说到时真正出货时这方面会作出改良；现时的卡扣设是想可以让用家容易点换电，但又要卡得到可负担到重型武器两把大斧的重量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257739" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0309-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0412" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323688/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323688_86b1f82b9b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0412" width="1024" height="624" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>其中，胸口和腿部的灯光效果表现优秀，亮度充足，光线分布均匀。然而，头部和手臂的灯光效果则稍显逊色。真三一还附带了一些特效配件，如可发光的烈阳闪光弹，增加了摆 pose 的趣味性。</p><p><a title="_DSC0334" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938528675/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938528675_432f6ac23d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0334" width="1024" height="642" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0340-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0340-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0340-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257728" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0347-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0347-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0347-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257729" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0348-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0348-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0348-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257730" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0349-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0349-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0349-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0350-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0351-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>可动性方面，这部真三一表现达到中上程度。虽然某些部位的活动范围有限，但整体来说足以应对大多数常见 Pose。值得一赞的是，真三一万能侠大量采用了齿轮结构，大大提升了关节的稳定性，带来了极佳的把玩手感，小编就特别喜爱这种跳齿式关节了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0324-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0328-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>配件方面，真三一配备了多种配件，包括标志性的真三一战斧和真三一镰刀。这些武器尺寸夸张，造型霸气，能够有效增强真三一的视觉冲击力。另一个值得一提的配件是重达 2 公斤的展示地台，地台采用了动画中 Invader 的造型，增加了展示效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-694x337.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="337" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-694x337.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0352-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-694x358.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-694x358.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0354-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257736" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-694x360.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-694x360.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0355-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257737" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-694x486.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="486" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-694x486.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0420-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257738" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-694x429.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="429" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-694x429.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0421-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC0386 (1)" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938073351/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938073351_898b539fa0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0386 (1)" width="1024" height="623" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0361" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938323738/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938323738_fa764d4e3d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0361" width="966" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0408" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53938406619/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53938406619_a65da83f4f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0408" width="848" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0372" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53937169757/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53937169757_1e86d35c68_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0372" width="1024" height="650" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>这款模寿与 BLITZWAY 合作的真三一万能侠是一个有潜力的作品，它在造型设计、部分灯光效果和稳定性等方面表现出色，为真三一万能侠爱好者提供了一个不错的选择。而大约 HK$1,1xx 的定价，可说是高性价比了。不过，如果能够简化地台以降低价格，可能更能提升吸引力。</p><p><a title="_DSC0340" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53937169737/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53937169737_25e37fa097_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0340" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br />
